videos.description: Sagaba Konate denies PJ Washington at the rim leading to a Jevon Carter 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Konate block leads to Carter 3

videos.description: WVU's Sagaba Konate forces a missed dunk on defense and then throws it down with two hands on the other end.
videos.headline: Konate rocks rim early

videos.description: Kevin Knox keeps Kentucky close early with back-to-back dunks.
videos.headline: Knox jams back-to-back dunks

videos.description: Sagaba Konate gets another block, this time on Kevin Knox against the backboard.
videos.headline: Konate pins one against the boards

videos.description: Sagaba Konate denies Jarred Vanderbilt setting up Jevon Carter for the fastbreak layup.
videos.headline: Konate blocks, Carter scores

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo knocks down an open 3-pointer to make it a 7-point game for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Diallo cuts into WVU's lead with 3

videos.description: Kevin Knox is left all alone for a 3-pointer to make it 56-50 as the Wildcats close the gap.
videos.headline: Knox makes it a 6-point game with 3

videos.description: Kentucky takes a 58-56 lead with a fast-break hammer from Kevin Knox.
videos.headline: Knox gives UK lead with fast-break dunk

videos.description: James Bolden gets the Mountaineers back in front with back-to-back 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Bolden hits back-to-back 3's for WVU

videos.description: James Bolden knocks down a 3-pointer to tie it at 74.
videos.headline: Bolden ties it with 3 for WVU

videos.description: Kevin Knox knocks down his fifth 3-pointer to put the Wildcats back in front 77-74.
videos.headline: Knox answers with a 3 for WVU

videos.description: Nick Richards gets the putback dunk uncontested at the rim to put Kentucky up 5 late against WVU.
videos.headline: Richards gets the putback dunk for UK

videos.description: Kevin Knox scores 34 points to fuel the Wildcats to an 83-76 victory on the road against the No. 7 Mountaineers.
videos.headline: Kentucky takes down No. 7 West Virginia

videos.description: Kentucky freshman Kevin Knox says his team just kept fighting in their second half comeback against the Mountaineers and that people counted them out facing the number 7 team in the country.
videos.headline: Knox: 'We gotta prove people wrong'
